import style from './nav.module.css';
import Search from "../search/Search.jsx"

 function Nav(props) {
   return (
      <main className={style.nav}>
         <section>
            <Search/>
         </section>
         <section>
            <select  className={style.desplegable} defaultValue="Filtrar" > 
               <option disabled value="Filtrar">
                  Origin
               </option>
            <option value="API">From API</option>
            <option value="DB">From DataBase</option>
            </select>

            <select  className={style.desplegable} defaultValue="Filtrar" > 
               <option disabled value="Filtrar">
                  Genre
               </option>
            <option value="API">From API</option>
            <option value="DB">From DataBase</option>
            </select>
         </section>
         
      </main>
   );
}

export default Nav;
